     <text id="A3053T">
          <front id="d2">
               <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                    <p>Hanger writes to his cousin, the Reverend John Miller, asking to borrow
                         several dollars.</p>
               </div1>
          </front>

          <body id="d4">
               <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                    <head>
                         <name type="recipient">Rev John Miller<lb/>York Pennsylvania</name>
                         <name type="place">Fort Delaware</name>
                    </head>

                    <opener>
                         <dateline>
                              <date value="1864-12-09">December 9th 1864</date>
                         </dateline>
                         <salute>Dear <orig reg="Cousin">Cousen</orig></salute>
                    </opener>

                    <p> for the first time since I have been a Prisoner I take the present
                         opportunity of writing you a few lines to let you know where I am &amp;
                         how I am I am well at the present and have been a prisoner since the 12th
                         of May last and I stand in need of many little articles which I cannot get
                         without the money and would like very much if you would send me a few
                         dollars if you can spare it conveniently and I will pay you back if it is
                         ever in my power. the folks were all well at home when I last heard from
                         them when you write direct to<lb/> William H. Hanger<lb/>
                         <abbr expan="Company">Co</abbr> E 5th <abbr expan="Virginia">Va</abbr>
                         infantry<lb/> Prisoner of War at <abbr expan="Fort">Ft</abbr> Delaware<lb/>
                         Division <abbr expan="Number">No.</abbr> 4<lb/> in care of <abbr
                              expan="Captain">Capt</abbr> G.W. Ahl on attached envelope </p>

                    <closer>
                         <salute/>
                         <signed>William H. Hanger</signed>
                         <seg type="postscript">[on reverse of letter] <abbr expan="Reverend">Rev.</abbr>
                              <abbr expan="John">J.</abbr> Miller York <abbr expan="Pennsylvania"
                              >Pa</abbr></seg>
                    </closer>
               </div1>
          </body>
     </text>
